STATE of North Carolina
v.
Dwayne Hoyte DOCKERY No. 463P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 16, 2017 Dwayne H. Dockery, for Dockery, Dwayne Hoyte. Mary Carla Babb, Assistant Attorney General, Todd Williams, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 21st of December 2016 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Buncombe County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 16th of March 2017."

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 21st of December 2016 by Defendant to Appoint Counsel:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference, this the 16th of March 2017."
